            sage: L(y^9).nth_root(-9)
            1/x*y

        This also works for inseparable extensions::

            sage: K.<x> = FunctionField(GF(3))
            sage: R.<y> = K[]
            sage: L.<y> = K.extension(y^3 - x^2)
            sage: L(x).nth_root(3)^3
            x
            sage: L(x^9).nth_root(-27)^-27
            x^9

