        base field is perfect, then this uses the algorithm described in
        Corollary 3 of [GiTr1996]_.

        .. SEEALSO::

            :meth:`is_nth_power`

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: K.<x> = FunctionField(GF(3))
            sage: f = (x+1)/(x+2)
